data.description: Great location...zoned RMD-A with several commercial businesses close by.  House sits on a corner lot with a detached two car garage.  HOUSE BEING SOLD AS IS AND NEEDS RENOVATIONS.  HVAC does not work. The house has some hardwood floors and has great bones.  With some remodeling this will make a great property.  Walk into the large living/dining room and step into a very large kitchen with laundry access.  House is off grade and would be easy to add additional bathroom.  SELLER MAKING NO REPAIRS TO THIS PROPERTY.
